6) Health Loading (Alochol, tobacco, smoking,BMI,Asthma,Diabetes, Hyperlipidemia,Hypothyroidism,Hypertension) :

9) Health Loading Mother :No
10) Health Loading Child :No
11) Health Loading Child :No

13) Stamp Duty: (Highest sum insured/1000)* Rs. 0.10/- {Considering that premium for per 1000/- sum insured is more than Rs. 2.50/-}
14) collection mode= Demand Draft (transit)
